{"type": "article", "id": 25032, "title": "同样是看美剧，这个西班牙设计师还原出了室内平面图", "description": "和手绘地图是一个道理，但也是一个巧妙的生意。", "date": "2016-04-06T14:27:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25894, "name": "平面图"}, {"id": 107, "name": "美剧"}, {"id": 8865, "name": "手绘"}, {"id": 25895, "name": "Iñaki Aliste Lizarralde"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 230, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125018QwBhNtpldEa6ykCL.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>将情景剧或电视剧中房子的平面图还原出来并不是一件难事，不少“模拟人生”的玩家都能直接建一个模型。西班牙室内设计师<a href=\"http://inakialistelizarralde.tumblr.com\"> Iñaki Aliste Lizarralde </a>就将《欲望都市》《飞屋环游记》《老友记》等十几个剧中的平面图手绘出来，添加上剧中出现的家具，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/es/shop/TVFLOORPLANSandMORE\">正在 ETSY 上售卖</a>。</p>\n<p>这些图片都有着看似严谨的结构和比例，每一面墙的厚薄都非常清晰，遵循了专业图纸的要求。不过，里面的家具和装饰都用彩铅画出来的，家具的颜色跳跃而绚丽，非常少女。设计师不忘画出光线透过窗户对房间色彩的影响，有了斜向的深浅阴影变化，让房间显得格外整洁干净。有点怀念起剧中有些凌乱的生活气息。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>设计师 Iñaki Aliste Lizarralde 起初制作了《欢乐一家亲》（Frasier）的平面图作为礼物送人，后来有人向他要其他电视剧的平面图。他通常将整部剧下载下来仔细看，而大部分时候房间的样子甚至家具都是不会改变的，只是浴室厨房会有调整，他也会灵活处理。而这些平面图是完全手绘的，没有使用 3D 建模技术，“用温暖而粗糙的手绘表达房子中的个性”。</p>\n<p class=\"\">以下是平面图，在英语中“ground floor”通常指底楼，“first floor”是底楼上的一层，即二楼。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125010PoJ1HC7sfS3WuLA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125011DNQMXOAYZgizaTou.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《飞屋环游记》（up）</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125011Zmxts4GfEgYnABPD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44300144\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《飞屋环游记》（up）</p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125012meUOIP9E1Hu4LiDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125012ABV6FfMcKTDmohZr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.69204738\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《辛普森一家》(The Simpsons)</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125013aHZEKru3T0zxmD2Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《老友记》（Friends）中 Monica 和 Rachel 的房间</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212501350sP9LeJKO8b4UmZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《老友记》（Friends）中 Chandler 和 Joey的房间</p>\n<p></p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125014VJS3lRLhA8fw4GWn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87207031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《欲望都市》（Sex &amp; The City）Carrie Bradshaw的房间</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125015JCw9IM3BEU8nazvD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46396396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《欲望都市》（Sex &amp; The City）Carrie Bradshaw的房间</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125015vVMgZrhiNc9bWTA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>《玛丽·泰勒·摩尔秀》( The Mary Tyler Moore Show)</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125016fTBeoW86OKMZqwuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《好汉两个半》Two and a Half Men</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125016AGHmXdxay3Zb0ON9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《黄金女郎 》The Golden Girls</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021250174MxqYPlifLkyNGDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25786164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《宋飞正传》（Seinfeld）</p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125017cjI18B5bQMzyfH2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">《欢乐一家亲》（Frasier）</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://inakialistelizarralde.tumblr.com/\">Iñaki Aliste Lizarralde</a>、<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/784955/the-waterfront-pavilion-australian-national-maritime-museum-fjmt-studio\">archdaily</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"></div>\n\n"}